3. Atmospheric
Purpose 
Stores daily and historical UV Index, dust, and optical depth from the Open-Meteo API
Greenhouse Gases Data Includs: 
•	UV Index
•	Aerosol Optical Depth
•	Dust
Table Structure
Column Name	Data Type	Key	Description
time	TIMESTAMP	Primary Key	Date and time of data entry 
uv_index	NUMERIC(4, 1)   		EPA measurement
aerosol_optical_depth   	NUMERIC(6, 4)   		EPA measurement
dust	NUMERIC(7, 2)		EPA measurement


4. Daily Summary
Purpose 
The daily summary table provides the user with a summary of the average and the max value for each variable in each table. 
Daily Summary Data Includs: 
•	time
•	summary_id
•	location_id
•	summary_date
Relationships
Summary Date is the date the report is created and not the date included in the time
Time - One-to-many 
Data Sources
All data is sourced from the Open-Meteo API and downloaded into a CSV file. 
•	This API includes 2 months of historical data and 5 days of forecast data
•	All gasses, API, PMs, and atmospheric measurements follow the United States Environmental Protection Agency standards. 


